@startuml
title UC010 - Control Flow Diagram (Display Car Park Reviews)
start

:1. User requests to view reviews;
:2. Send request for car park reviews;

:3. Fetch car park data;
:4. Retrieve reviews for the selected car park;
if (5. Are reviews available?) then (yes)
  :6. Display reviews to the user;
  --> [Success]
else (no)
  :7. Display message: "No reviews available";
  --> [Retry]
endif

stop
@enduml
